[Episodio 21]

00:01:49.310 --> 00:01:50.190
Hola, Directora Jiang.

00:01:55.030 --> 00:01:55.950
Lo hice yo.

00:01:57.670 --> 00:01:59.310
Me lo ordenó Fu Xizhou,

00:02:00.110 --> 00:02:02.830
