00:02:15.110 --> 00:02:15.710
Fu Xizhou,

00:02:15.830 --> 00:02:17.350
eres despreciable.

00:02:20.790 --> 00:02:21.910
¿Te volviste loca?

00:02:22.270 --> 00:02:23.670
